#. Tag: date
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "2003-03-08"
msgstr "२००३-०३-०८"

#. Tag: manvolnum
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid "<manvolnum>1</manvolnum>"
msgstr "<मन्वोल्नुम्>१</मन्वोल्नुम्>"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates <filename>Makefile.in</filename> and <filename>Makefile</filename> "
"from a <filename>Makefile.am</filename>"
msgstr ""
"<filename>Makefile.in</filename> तथा <filename>Makefile</filename> इत्येतत् "
"<filename>Makefile.am</filename> इत्यस्मात् निर्माति"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>create_makefile</command> <group><replaceable>relativepath/"
"Makefile</replaceable></group> <group><replaceable>relativepath</"
"replaceable></group>"
msgstr ""
"<command>create_makefile</command> <group><replaceable>relativepath/"
"Makefile</replaceable></group> <समूह><प्रतिस्थापनीय>सापेक्षमार्ग</replaceable></"
"group>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "वर्णनम्‌"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>create_makefile</command> creates the <filename>Makefile.in</"
"filename> and <filename>Makefile</filename> in a subdirectory containing a "
"<filename>Makefile.am</filename>. This script saves time compared to re-"
"running configure completely"
msgstr ""
"<command>create_makefile</command> <filename>Makefile.am</filename> इति "
"उपनिर्देशिकायां <filename>Makefile.in</filename> तथा <filename>Makefile</"
"filename> इत्येतत् निर्माति । एषा स्क्रिप्ट् पूर्णतया विन्यासस्य पुनः चालनस्य तुलने समयस्य "
"रक्षणं करोति"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that you must supply the path to the desired <filename>Makefile</"
"filename> <filename>Makefile.am</filename> (though the final <filename>/"
"Makefile</filename> may be omitted)."
msgstr ""
"ध्यानं कुर्वन्तु यत् भवद्भिः इष्टस्य <filename>Makefile</filename> <filename>Makefile."
"am</filename> इत्यस्य मार्गस्य आपूर्तिः करणीयः (यद्यपि अन्तिमः <filename>/Makefile</"
"filename> लोपः भवितुम् अर्हति) ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This script may be run from the toplevel directory (the one containing "
"<filename>configure</filename>) or from one of it's subdirectories."
msgstr ""
"इयं स्क्रिप्ट् toplevel निर्देशिकातः (<filename>configure</filename> इति युक्तात्) "
"अथवा अस्य उपनिर्देशिकाभ्यः एकस्मात् चालयितुं शक्यते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the source directory is different from the build directory (see the "
"environment variables below), it will be assumed that the <filename>Makefile."
"am</filename> and <filename>Makefile.in</filename> belong beneath the source "
"directory and that the <filename>Makefile</filename> belongs beneath the "
"build directory."
msgstr ""
"यदि स्रोतनिर्देशिका निर्माणनिर्देशिकातः भिन्ना अस्ति (अधः वातावरणचराः पश्यन्तु), तर्हि "
"<filename>Makefile.am</filename> तथा <filename>Makefile.in</filename> "
"स्रोतनिर्देशिकायाः अधः सन्ति इति कल्प्यते तथा च <filename>Makefile</filename> इति "
"निर्माणनिर्देशिकायाः अधः अस्ति इति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "This utility is part of the &kde; Software Development Kit."
msgstr "एषा उपयोगिता &kde; सॉफ्टवेयर विकास किट।"

#. Tag: title
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "Environment"
msgstr "पर्यावरणम्‌"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"One of the following variables (but not both) should be set if the source "
"directory is different from the build directory. If the build directory is "
"simply a subdirectory of the source directory, the simpler variable "
"<envar>OBJ_SUBDIR</envar> should be used."
msgstr ""
"यदि स्रोतनिर्देशिका build निर्देशिकातः भिन्ना अस्ति तर्हि निम्नलिखितचरानाम् एकः (किन्तु "
"उभयत्र न) सेट् कर्तव्यः । यदि build निर्देशिका केवलं स्रोतनिर्देशिकायाः उपनिर्देशिका अस्ति "
"तर्हि सरलतरं चरं <envar>OBJ_SUBDIR</envar> उपयोक्तव्यम् ।"

#. Tag: envar
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "OBJ_SUBJDIR"
msgstr "OBJ_SUBJDIR"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Indicates that the build directory is in the given subdirectory of the "
"source directory. For instance, if the source directory is <filename class="
"\"directory\">kdesdk</filename> and the build directory is <filename class="
"\"directory\">kdesdk/obj-i386-linux</filename>, then <envar>OBJ_SUBDIR</"
"envar> should be set to <parameter>obj-i386-linux</parameter>."
msgstr ""
"build directory स्रोतनिर्देशिकायाः दत्ते उपनिर्देशिकायां अस्ति इति सूचयति । यथा, यदि "
"स्रोतनिर्देशिका <filename class=\"directory\">kdesdk</filename> अस्ति तथा च "
"निर्माणनिर्देशिका <filename class=\"directory\">kdesdk/obj-i386-linux</"
"filename> अस्ति, तर्हि <envar> OBJ_SUBDIR</envar> इत्येतत् <parameter>obj-i386-"
"linux</parameter> इति सेट् कर्तव्यम् ।"

#. Tag: envar
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "OBJ_REPLACEMENT"
msgstr "OBJ_REPLACEMENT इति"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A <command>sed</command> expression that is used to transform the source "
"directory into the build directory. For instance, if the source directory is "
"<filename class=\"directory\">~/src/kdesdk</filename> and the build "
"directory is <filename class=\"directory\">~/src/kdesdk-obj</filename>, then "
"<envar>OBJ_REPLACEMENT</envar> should be set to <parameter>s#kdesdk#kdesdk-"
"obj#</parameter>."
msgstr ""
"एकं <command>sed</command> व्यञ्जनं यत् स्रोतनिर्देशिकायाः निर्माणनिर्देशिकायां "
"परिवर्तनार्थं उपयुज्यते । यथा, यदि स्रोतनिर्देशिका <filename class=\"directory\">~/"
"src/kdesdk</filename> अस्ति तथा च निर्माणनिर्देशिका <filename class=\"directory"
"\">~/src/kdesdk-obj</filename> अस्ति, तर्हि ततः <envar>OBJ_REPLACEMENT</envar> "
"इत्येतत् <parameter>s#kdesdk#kdesdk-obj#</parameter> इति सेट् कर्तव्यम् ।"

#. Tag: title
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "See Also"
msgstr "इदमपि पश्यन्तु"

